#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.isin.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.isin"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:1 of
msgid "Whether elements in Series are contained in `values`."
msgstr "Series 中的元素是否包含在 `values` 中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:3 of
msgid ""
"Return a boolean Series showing whether each element in the Series "
"matches an element in the passed sequence of `values` exactly."
msgstr ""
"返回一个布尔 Series，显示 Series 中的每个元素是否与传入的 `values` 序列中"
"的某个元素完全匹配。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:6 of
msgid ""
"The sequence of values to test. Passing in a single string will raise a "
"``TypeError``. Instead, turn a single string into a list of one element."
msgstr ""
"用于测试的值序列。传入单个字符串将引发 ``TypeError``。应将单个字符串转换"
"为只包含一个元素的列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:11 of
msgid "Series of booleans indicating if each element is in values."
msgstr "布尔 Series，表示每个元素是否在 values 中。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:14 of
msgid "* If `values` is a string"
msgstr "* 如果 `values` 是字符串"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:14 of
msgid "If `values` is a string"
msgstr "如果 `values` 是字符串"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.isin`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:19 of
msgid "Equivalent method on DataFrame."
msgstr "DataFrame 上的等效方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:22 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.isin.series_isin:35 of
msgid ""
"Passing a single string as ``s.isin('lame')`` will raise an error. Use a "
"list of one element instead:"
msgstr ""
"传入单个字符串如 ``s.isin('lame')`` 将引发错误。应使用只包含一个元素的"
"列表代替："

